name: Rage Machine
details:
Agressive distortionWide variety of heavy metal style distortion tones, Two EQ knobs allow you to shape the tone dramatically and a level knob allows you to dial in the precise amount of distortion you want on your leads. Its full metal casing makes it durable and road ready, and like most great effects pedals it has true bypass.
Many distortion tones
Full metal shell
Pedalboard friendly
True bypass

Input: 1/4" monaural jack (impedance: 470k Ohms)
Output: 1/4" monaural jack (impedance: 100 Ohms)
Power Requirements: AC adapter 9V DC (center minus plug)
Current Draw: 128 mA
Dimensions: 1.6535" (W) x 2.0472" (H) x 3.6811" (D)
Weight: 0.36lb
